==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Undeceive
<hw>Un`de*ceive"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>deceive</ets>.]</ety> <def>To cause to be no
longer deceived; to free from deception, fraud, fallacy, or
mistake.</def> <rj><au>South.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Undecency</ent>⟦br⟧
